    ChatPanel
    Panel that shows and send the players'messages.
    PlayerPanel
    Panel intended to go into the Panel on the right of the Board and to show the card of the current player.
    PlayingPlayersButton
    Class to represent the bottom-panel of the playing window.
    TitlePanel
    Panel representing the upper part of the screen (the title part) containing the button to activate and turn off the audio and the undo button.
